    },
    {
      "content": "<bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>A:<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept> Yes, when users register data using the Password Reset Registration Portal it gets saved into private authentication fields that are only visible by Global Administrators and the user himself.",
      "pos": [
