      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "<bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>A:<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept> A user is considered registered when he or she has at least N pieces of authentication info defined, where N is the Number of Authentication Methods Required that you have set in the <bpt id=\"p2\">[</bpt>Azure Management Portal<ept id=\"p2\">](https://manage.windowsazure.com)</ept>.",
