      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "<bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>A:<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept> Email, SMS messages, and phone calls should arrive in under 1 minute, with the normal case being 5-20 seconds.",
      "pos": [
        4643,
        4760
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "If you do not receive the notification in this timeframe, check your junk folder, that the number / email being contacted is the one you expect, and that the authentication data in the directory is correctly formatted.",
      "pos": [
        4761,
