    },
    {
      "content": "Q:  What parts of the password reset experience get branded when I set organizational branding in my directory’s configure tab?",
      "pos": [
        5776,
        5903
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "<bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>A:<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept> The password reset portal will show your organizational logo and will also allow you to configure the Contact your administrator link to point to a custom email or URL.",
      "pos": [
        5911,
        6086
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "Any email that gets sent by password reset will include your organization’s logo, colors (in this case red), name in the body of the email, and customized from name.",
      "pos": [
