      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "<bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>A:<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept> You can send your users to https://passwordreset.microsoftonline.com directly, or you can instruct them to click on the Can’t access your account link found on any School or Work ID sign in screen.",
      "pos": [
        6467,
        6671
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "You can feel free to publish these links (or create URL redirects to them) in any place that is easily accessible to your users.",
      "pos": [
