      ],
      "content": "<bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>A:<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept> You can configure up to 20 custom security questions in the <bpt id=\"p2\">[</bpt>Azure Management Portal<ept id=\"p2\">](https://manage.windowsazure.com)</ept>."
