      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "<bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>A:<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept> Yes, one limit can be set for registration and another for reset.",
      "pos": [
        8725,
        8797
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "3-5 security questions may be required for registration and 3-5 may be required for reset.",
      "pos": [
        8798,
        8888
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "Q:  If a user has registered more than the maximum number of questions required to reset, how are security questions selected during reset?",
      "pos": [
        8895,
        9034
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "<bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>A:<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept> N security questions are selected at random out of the total number of questions a user has registered for, where N is the minimum number of questions required for password reset.",
      "pos": [
        9042,
        9228
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "For example, if a user has 5 security questions registered, but only 3 are required to reset, 3 of those 5 will be selected randomly and presented to the user at the time of reset.",
      "pos": [
        9229,
        9409
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "If the user gets the answers to the questions wrong, the selection process re-occurs to prevent question hammering.",
      "pos": [
        9410,
        9525
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "Q:  Do you prevent users from attempting password reset many times in a short time period?",
      "pos": [
        9532,
        9622
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "<bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>A:<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept> Yes, there are several security features built into password reset.",
      "pos": [
        9630,
        9704
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "Users may only try 5 password reset attempts within an hour before being locked out for 24 hours.",
      "pos": [
        9705,
        9802
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "Users may only try to validate a phone number 5 times within an hour before being locked out for 24 hours.",
      "pos": [
        9803,
        9909
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "Users may only try a single authentication method 5 times within an hour before being locked out for 24 hours.",
      "pos": [
        9910,
        10020
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "Q:  For how long are the email and SMS one-time passcode valid?",
      "pos": [
