    },
    {
      "content": "<bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>A:<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept> See How Password Writeback works for a detailed explanation of what happens when you enable Password Writeback, as well as how data flows through the system back into your on-premises environment.",
      "pos": [
